citation: Proclamation under the Legislation Publication Act 1996 (Tas)
text:
Proclamation under the Legislation Publication Act 1996

I, the Governor in and over the State of Tasmania and its Dependencies in the Commonwealth of Australia, acting with the advice of the Executive Council, by this my proclamation made under section 2 of the Legislation Publication Act 1996 fix 23 March 1998 as the day on which that Act commences.

11 March 1998

G.S.M. GREEN

Governor

By His Excellency's Command,

TONY RUNDLE

Premier

Displayed and numbered in accordance with the Rules Publication Act 1953.

Notified in the Gazette on 18 March 1998

This proclamation is administered in the Department of Premier and Cabinet.
